WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.001 --> 00:00:03.003
Previously. on <i>The Testaments...</i>

2
00:00:03.086 --> 00:00:05.130
The Aunts decide our contenders today.

3
00:00:05.214 --> 00:00:06.840
<i>Two to three suitors each. usually.</i>

4
00:00:06.924 --> 00:00:08.675
<i>Then house visits.
Then weddings.</i>

5
00:00:08.759 --> 00:00:10.594
Then prison for the rest of our lives.

6
00:00:10.677 --> 00:00:12.763
Your matches are a success.

7
00:00:12.846 --> 00:00:14.431
This is Commander Weston.

8
00:00:14.514 --> 00:00:16.391
This is the Commander to impress.

9
00:00:16.475 --> 00:00:18.352
Is this it?
I'm in love.

10
00:00:18.435 --> 00:00:20.145
- Who?
- Garth.

11
00:00:20.229 --> 00:00:22.940
Commander Olson has a beachfront
property with over 50 acres.

12
00:00:23.023 --> 00:00:25.692
but Commander Pierce
has a 10 handicap in golf.

13
00:00:25.776 --> 00:00:27.778
Agnes. who did you get?

14
00:00:27.861 --> 00:00:30.739
Commander Pritzger.
Commander Riley. and Commander Weston.

15
00:00:30.822 --> 00:00:32.866
Weston runs the Eyes. my Martha says.

16
00:00:32.950 --> 00:00:36.245
- Have you gotten any matches?
- Commander Chapin.

17
00:00:36.328 --> 00:00:38.497
- Who is he?
- My Guardian.

18
00:00:38.580 --> 00:00:41.124
- Please don't marry him.
- I don't get to choose any of this!

19
00:00:41.208 --> 00:00:43.001
I don't want to marry anyone!

20
00:00:43.085 --> 00:00:45.671
- He's your match. right?
- Yeah. That's him.

21
00:00:45.754 --> 00:00:47.839
<i>They're investigating
the Mayday attack.</i>

22
00:00:47.923 --> 00:00:49.007
I overheard my father this morning.

23
00:00:49.091 --> 00:00:51.260
No. no. no. no. no! No. no!

24
00:00:53.262 --> 00:00:55.931
I have my first Green appointment today
with the tailor.

25
00:00:56.014 --> 00:00:58.225
And then soon.
your dad to get my teeth whitened.

26
00:00:58.767 --> 00:01:01.061
<i>You are not blameless. girls!</i>

27
00:01:01.144 --> 00:01:04.356
<i>Shame upon any of you that tempt a man!</i>

28
00:01:05.649 --> 00:01:07.985
Did you have a nice visit with Becka?

29
00:01:10.028 --> 00:01:12.990
<i>I have to say.
Agnes is very impressive.</i>

30
00:01:13.073 --> 00:01:14.825
Is there anything you'd like to ask me?

31
00:01:14.908 --> 00:01:19.621
I only hope I can measure up
to your expectations of a wife.

32
00:01:34.052 --> 00:01:36.930
<i>♪ Anyone who's ever had a heart ♪</i>

33
00:01:39.725 --> 00:01:41.935
<i>♪ Wouldn't turn around and break it ♪</i>

34
00:01:45.397 --> 00:01:48.191
<i>♪ And anyone who's ever played a part ♪</i>

35
00:01:51.236 --> 00:01:53.572
<i>♪ Wouldn't turn around and hate it ♪</i>

36
00:01:55.449 --> 00:01:57.200
<i>I had a rich fantasy life.</i>

37
00:01:59.077 --> 00:02:01.246
<i>Even in Gilead. that was possible.</i>

38
00:02:02.247 --> 00:02:05.459
<i>The only difference here was that
I believed that God knew about it.</i>

39
00:02:06.251 --> 00:02:07.627
<i>And judged me.</i>

40
00:02:07.711 --> 00:02:11.048
<i>♪ Oh. sweet. sweet Jane ♪</i>

41
00:02:14.384 --> 00:02:18.722
<i>♪ Heavenly wine and roses ♪</i>

42
00:02:18.805 --> 00:02:22.684
<i>♪ Seem to whisper to me ♪</i>

43
00:02:23.310 --> 00:02:25.604
<i>♪ When you smile ♪</i>

44
00:02:26.146 --> 00:02:28.148
<i>♪ When you smile ♪</i>

45
00:02:28.899 --> 00:02:30.525
<i>♪ When you smile ♪</i>

46
00:02:35.739 --> 00:02:37.741
<i>Becka was going to marry Garth.</i>

47
00:02:38.867 --> 00:02:42.120
<i>I wasn't supposed to know yet.
but Paula let it slip.</i>

48
00:02:42.204 --> 00:02:44.456
<i>so I found out before the others.</i>

49
00:02:45.666 --> 00:02:47.751
<i>When I first heard.
my chest started burning</i>

50
00:02:47.834 --> 00:02:50.003
<i>like I was swallowing hot wax.</i>

51
00:02:50.921 --> 00:02:53.340
<i>Like I was being scraped raw
from the inside.</i>

52
00:02:54.549 --> 00:02:55.926
<i>I guess I was.</i>

53
00:02:58.929 --> 00:03:02.724
<i>♪ La-la-la-la. la-la-la ♪</i>

54
00:03:05.394 --> 00:03:07.437
<i>But I couldn't be angry at Becka.</i>

55
00:03:07.521 --> 00:03:09.147
<i>She didn't have a choice.</i>

56
00:03:10.482 --> 00:03:11.775
<i>None of us did.</i>

57
00:03:16.613 --> 00:03:17.823
Praise be.

58
00:03:18.532 --> 00:03:21.201
<i>Welcome to my engagement.
Praise be His mercy.</i>

59
00:03:21.284 --> 00:03:23.412
Masterfully done.

60
00:03:24.788 --> 00:03:28.041
<i>I have to glue the plate back
together before my wedding.</i>

61
00:03:28.125 --> 00:03:32.295
<i>The remade plate is more precious
because it's been lovingly restored.</i>

62
00:03:32.379 --> 00:03:35.048
<i>Destruction and resurrection.</i>

63
00:03:36.425 --> 00:03:38.343
Congratulations on your betrothal.

64
00:03:38.427 --> 00:03:39.469
Sweetheart.

65
00:03:40.637 --> 00:03:42.597
Okay. picture time!

66
00:03:43.348 --> 00:03:44.891
- Come on.
- Guess I'm up.

67
00:03:44.975 --> 00:03:47.060
Yes. yes. right over there.

68
00:03:47.144 --> 00:03:48.770
- And. dear. right here.
- Yes.

69
00:03:49.438 --> 00:03:50.480
Looking good.

70
00:03:50.564 --> 00:03:53.775
<i>I was to enter marriage
a properly broken woman.</i>

71
00:03:54.651 --> 00:03:56.528
<i>Just as God meant me to be.</i>

72
00:03:58.989 --> 00:04:00.699
<i>Just as my husband expected.</i>

73
00:04:15.755 --> 00:04:16.965
Blessed day.

74
00:04:19.342 --> 00:04:21.136
And congratulations...

75
00:04:24.556 --> 00:04:25.932
on your engagement.

76
00:04:27.434 --> 00:04:28.477
Thanks.

77
00:04:30.270 --> 00:04:31.438
Same to you.

78
00:04:33.523 --> 00:04:34.941
He's blessed us both.

79
00:04:40.781 --> 00:04:41.948
Blessed day.

80
00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:07.557
Blessed day! Who'd you get?

81
00:05:07.641 --> 00:05:08.975
Silence!

82
00:05:09.768 --> 00:05:11.895
Come along. girls. In we go.

83
00:05:18.235 --> 00:05:20.445
You won't be following Agnes today.

84
00:05:20.529 --> 00:05:22.447
Wha... What? Why not?

85
00:05:22.906 --> 00:05:24.741
Curiosity is the Devil at work.

86
00:05:24.825 --> 00:05:26.409
You'll be down the hall today.

87
00:05:29.538 --> 00:05:33.166
You too. Shunammite.
Off you go. the both of you.

88
00:05:34.751 --> 00:05:36.086
Hm.

89
00:05:37.546 --> 00:05:38.797
Why are we in trouble?

90
00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:40.924
Copulation class. Must be.

91
00:05:41.508 --> 00:05:42.509
Oh.

92
00:05:42.592 --> 00:05:44.219
Eligible girls only.

93
00:05:44.302 --> 00:05:46.179
But I'm sure you know
all about that stuff.

94
00:05:46.888 --> 00:05:49.766
Yeah. I know about copulation.

95
00:05:50.058 --> 00:05:51.852
I don't need to tell you. though.

96
00:05:52.394 --> 00:05:54.521
You seem to know everything.

97
00:05:57.774 --> 00:05:59.734
Do you know what happened to Talia?

98
00:05:59.818 --> 00:06:01.778
The Pearl Girl who was taken by the Eyes?

99
00:06:02.279 --> 00:06:03.947
She won't be back.

100
00:06:05.615 --> 00:06:08.034
But. what if she didn't do anything wrong?

101
00:06:09.369 --> 00:06:12.038
Well. if the Eyes took her.
then she did something wrong.

102
00:06:13.498 --> 00:06:16.459
Come on. We have a lame class to get to.

103
00:06:21.548 --> 00:06:24.009
<i>We had waited
so long to hear this.</i>

104
00:06:24.092 --> 00:06:25.719
<i>The mysteries of life.</i>

105
00:06:25.802 --> 00:06:27.804
<i>The mysteries of marriage.</i>

106
00:06:28.555 --> 00:06:31.391
<i>What would happen when we
shared a bed with our husbands?</i>

107
00:06:32.267 --> 00:06:37.105
Lord. please keep
these girls' minds free from sin today.

108
00:06:37.188 --> 00:06:39.858
To teach creation is a delicate path.

109
00:06:39.941 --> 00:06:42.444
and we endeavor to step
only where You wish.

110
00:06:42.527 --> 00:06:44.988
- Amen.
- Amen.

111
00:06:47.449 --> 00:06:50.410
God's Sacred Vessel.

112
00:06:50.869 --> 00:06:52.454
Each of you has one.

113
00:06:53.038 --> 00:06:55.040
This is where your baby will grow.

114
00:06:55.582 --> 00:06:57.208
But only if you are God-fearing girls

115
00:06:57.292 --> 00:06:59.794
and He chooses to bless you with child.

116
00:07:00.503 --> 00:07:01.671
On your wedding night.

117
00:07:01.755 --> 00:07:04.549
when it is time for you
to endeavor to create new life.

118
00:07:04.633 --> 00:07:06.760
your husband will instruct.

119
00:07:06.843 --> 00:07:08.094
and you will follow.

120
00:07:09.012 --> 00:07:12.098
As long as you stay meek and deferential.

121
00:07:12.182 --> 00:07:15.560
your husband will guide your hand
in your wifely duties

122
00:07:15.644 --> 00:07:16.978
as in all things.

123
00:07:17.854 --> 00:07:19.731
As Ephesians tells us.

124
00:07:20.482 --> 00:07:24.110
"Wives. you shall obey
your husband in everything.

125
00:07:24.694 --> 00:07:26.905
as you would obey the Lord."

126
00:07:29.658 --> 00:07:33.119
Now. let's move on to pregnancy
and prenatal nutrition.

127
00:07:33.703 --> 00:07:36.873
<i>Our education was left wanting.</i>

128
00:08:11.908 --> 00:08:13.410
What is taking you so long?

129
00:08:13.493 --> 00:08:14.828
I'll just be a minute.

130
00:08:16.996 --> 00:08:18.123
What's in there?

131
00:08:20.917 --> 00:08:21.918
You?!

132
00:08:24.254 --> 00:08:25.755
This isn't fair!

133
00:08:26.381 --> 00:08:28.299
Even a Pearl Girl
gets her period before I do?

134
00:08:28.383 --> 00:08:30.301
Why is God doing this to me?

135
00:08:30.385 --> 00:08:31.553
Please don't tell anyone.

136
00:08:31.636 --> 00:08:34.180
I'm the one who eats organic vegetables
and drinks clean water.

137
00:08:34.264 --> 00:08:35.807
and you...

138
00:08:35.890 --> 00:08:37.642
grew up in garbage!

139
00:08:38.143 --> 00:08:39.227
What are you doing?

140
00:08:39.310 --> 00:08:41.438
You have to show that to the Aunts
so that you can ring the bell.

141
00:08:41.521 --> 00:08:43.314
I c... I can't.

142
00:08:43.398 --> 00:08:44.607
They'll make me get married.

143
00:08:44.691 --> 00:08:46.151
Of course they will.

144
00:08:46.234 --> 00:08:47.902
Why do you think you're here. Daisy?

145
00:08:47.986 --> 00:08:48.987
On Earth?

146
00:08:49.070 --> 00:08:50.321
Shunammite...

147
00:08:50.405 --> 00:08:51.906
please don't tell anyone.

148
00:08:53.616 --> 00:08:54.993
Shunammite...

149
00:09:02.250 --> 00:09:04.044
When do you think Aunt Lydia
will make announcements?

150
00:09:05.211 --> 00:09:06.379
Mm.

151
00:09:11.885 --> 00:09:13.094
Are you okay?

152
00:09:14.679 --> 00:09:16.431
Yes. Pray. why wouldn't I be?

153
00:09:18.516 --> 00:09:20.143
Are you disappointed with your engagement?

154
00:09:26.232 --> 00:09:27.317
He's nice.

155
00:09:28.777 --> 00:09:31.946
He's fine.
He said maybe we could get a dog.

156
00:09:49.547 --> 00:09:50.757
What is it?

157
00:09:56.387 --> 00:09:58.932
I had a cleaning with Dr. Grove.

158
00:10:02.352 --> 00:10:04.145
- Never mind.
- No. what happened?

159
00:10:04.229 --> 00:10:06.314
Hulda. tell me.

160
00:10:06.981 --> 00:10:08.817
- Please.
- You won't say anything?

161
00:10:08.900 --> 00:10:10.151
I promise.

162
00:10:17.367 --> 00:10:19.160
He took my hand...

163
00:10:20.453 --> 00:10:21.746
and...

164
00:10:23.331 --> 00:10:25.583
he pressed it against his body.

165
00:10:28.753 --> 00:10:31.256
I didn't... I didn't know what to do.

166
00:10:34.008 --> 00:10:35.593
I betrayed the flesh and His word

167
00:10:35.677 --> 00:10:38.680
and now I'm gonna burn in Hell
for ever and ever and ever and ever.

168
00:10:38.763 --> 00:10:40.056
You need to tell the Aunts.

169
00:10:40.140 --> 00:10:42.517
No. No. I sinned. I...

170
00:10:44.144 --> 00:10:45.228
I tempted him.

171
00:10:45.311 --> 00:10:47.355
It's my fault. I lured him.

172
00:10:47.438 --> 00:10:49.524
I ensnared him with my body.
I ensnared Becka's dad.

173
00:10:49.607 --> 00:10:51.484
He's not supposed to do that.

174
00:10:52.944 --> 00:10:54.279
Only your husband is.

175
00:10:54.362 --> 00:10:56.197
You need to tell the Aunts.

176
00:10:56.281 --> 00:10:58.741
- They will help you!
- No. No. I can't!

177
00:10:58.825 --> 00:10:59.993
The Aunts. they'll freak out and...

178
00:11:00.076 --> 00:11:02.745
- They will help you.
- Everyone will know!

179
00:11:05.331 --> 00:11:06.624
"Be strong and courageous.

180
00:11:06.708 --> 00:11:09.294
Do not be afraid.
for the Lord God is with you."

181
00:11:11.087 --> 00:11:12.672
I'm with you. Hulda.

182
00:11:23.474 --> 00:11:25.602
<i>I bet you think I was being a real shit.</i>

183
00:11:26.603 --> 00:11:30.607
<i>I told myself I wasn't quite sure
what Dr. Grove had done to me.</i>

184
00:11:30.690 --> 00:11:33.193
<i>so Hulda had to be the one to speak out.</i>

185
00:11:35.278 --> 00:11:38.114
<i>Until Hulda.
I had been able to lie to myself.</i>

186
00:11:41.784 --> 00:11:43.953
<i>♪ Anyone who's ever had a heart ♪</i>

187
00:11:44.037 --> 00:11:46.456
Agnes?

188
00:11:46.539 --> 00:11:48.666
Agnes!

189
00:11:48.750 --> 00:11:50.627
Agnes. help me!

190
00:11:50.710 --> 00:11:51.711
I have to help her!

191
00:11:52.921 --> 00:11:54.589
I have to help her.

192
00:11:54.672 --> 00:11:56.216
I have to help her.

193
00:11:56.299 --> 00:11:57.342
Agnes?

194
00:11:57.425 --> 00:11:58.635
I have to help her!

195
00:12:05.225 --> 00:12:07.852
Bless us. oh God.
and these Thy gifts.

196
00:12:07.936 --> 00:12:10.521
which we are about to receive
from Thy bounty.

197
00:12:10.939 --> 00:12:12.774
Blessed be the fruit. girls.

198
00:12:13.149 --> 00:12:14.776
May the Lord open.

199
00:12:18.029 --> 00:12:21.824
When each of you first entered
the gates of this institution.

200
00:12:21.908 --> 00:12:23.534
it was with one goal in mind...

201
00:12:23.618 --> 00:12:24.911
- Is this a thing?
- Shh.

202
00:12:24.994 --> 00:12:27.580
...to prepare you for tomorrow.

203
00:12:27.664 --> 00:12:31.751
For marriage. Motherhood. Serving God.

204
00:12:32.293 --> 00:12:35.505
Today. we rejoice
for the daughters of Gilead

205
00:12:35.588 --> 00:12:37.966
who have taken that first step.

206
00:12:38.675 --> 00:12:42.595
Blessings on Constance Wickhem.
who is to marry Commander Moore...

207
00:12:44.889 --> 00:12:46.724
...on Jehosheba Yardarm.

208
00:12:46.808 --> 00:12:48.643
who is to marry Commander Caldwell.

209
00:12:48.726 --> 00:12:51.396
Praise be!

210
00:12:51.479 --> 00:12:53.481
Blessings on Rebecka Grove.

211
00:12:53.564 --> 00:12:56.234
who is to marry
soon-to-be Commander Chapin...

212
00:12:59.696 --> 00:13:03.241
...on Miriam Dawson.
who is to marry Commander Lewis...

213
00:13:03.324 --> 00:13:04.826
Commander Colonies.

214
00:13:06.244 --> 00:13:08.204
...on Hulda Marie Edwardson.

215
00:13:08.288 --> 00:13:10.373
who is to marry Commander Thomas.

216
00:13:15.253 --> 00:13:17.964
And blessings on Agnes MacKenzie.

217
00:13:18.047 --> 00:13:20.258
who is to wed Commander Weston.

218
00:13:20.341 --> 00:13:23.970
a man chosen by God to lead and protect.

219
00:13:27.056 --> 00:13:29.600
Congratulations on your betrothals.

220
00:13:29.684 --> 00:13:32.395
May the Lord bless you and keep you.

221
00:13:32.770 --> 00:13:34.230
Amen.

222
00:13:34.314 --> 00:13:36.774
Praise be His name.

223
00:13:37.525 --> 00:13:38.735
You all are engaged.

224
00:13:42.613 --> 00:13:43.614
We did it.

225
00:13:47.368 --> 00:13:49.328
Have you been
to Commander Thomas's house yet?

226
00:13:50.371 --> 00:13:51.456
Yes.

227
00:13:52.373 --> 00:13:54.167
- Is it big?
- Mm-hmm.

228
00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:56.044
Paula must love all the wedding planning.

229
00:13:57.295 --> 00:13:58.629
Yeah.

230
00:14:00.173 --> 00:14:03.384
My mom said Chapin's father was
a big Commander back in the day.

231
00:14:03.885 --> 00:14:05.636
The pedigree does matter. I guess.

232
00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:07.138
You dodged a bullet.

233
00:14:07.221 --> 00:14:08.681
They let me decide.

234
00:14:10.224 --> 00:14:11.225
I chose Garth.

235
00:14:12.852 --> 00:14:14.062
Garth?

236
00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:16.814
Guardian Chapin?

237
00:14:16.898 --> 00:14:18.691
He's my fiancé now.

238
00:14:19.400 --> 00:14:20.818
Congratulations.

239
00:14:20.902 --> 00:14:23.112
Does your Pearl Girl
always have to sit with us?

240
00:14:24.072 --> 00:14:25.239
She's my friend.

241
00:14:25.323 --> 00:14:28.201
Okay. why is everybody being so touchy?

242
00:14:28.993 --> 00:14:31.329
Today is supposed to be about having fun.

243
00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:33.790
Can't we just have fun?

244
00:14:36.292 --> 00:14:38.586
Who do you think is going to throw
the first engagement party?

245
00:14:38.669 --> 00:14:39.962
Me.

246
00:14:40.838 --> 00:14:43.049
The invitations are being
hand-delivered today.

247
00:14:43.591 --> 00:14:44.842
First party of the season.

248
00:14:45.176 --> 00:14:46.177
Nice.

249
00:15:06.280 --> 00:15:07.740
It's too cloying.

250
00:15:07.824 --> 00:15:11.452
You've tried seven cakes
and haven't liked a single bite.

251
00:15:12.453 --> 00:15:14.413
This tasting was a courtesy. Agnes.

252
00:15:15.331 --> 00:15:16.582
Commander. what do you think?

253
00:15:18.084 --> 00:15:20.044
Well. me...

254
00:15:20.128 --> 00:15:22.463
I like 'em all.
But. I have a bit of a sweet tooth.

255
00:15:22.547 --> 00:15:25.591
I'm really happy to keep
tasting samples. actually.

